F I V E ✨ 

just like that my baby is five! She’s spunky and oh so sweet. She makes me laugh and keeps me on my toes every day. She loves her big sister, friends, her animals and all our fosters. She loves school and is always the teachers helper. Though she’s the youngest on the whole dance team, she keeps up and I’m shocked by her ability. She loves to help me in the garden and in the kitchen. I’m so thankful for her caring heart, joyful spirit and fiery personality (even if she likes to put my patience to the test 😂). I can’t wait to see what year 6 brings and I am so thankful God made me her mama! Happy birthday my sweet girl! We all love you so much Palmer Jean! #thisis5 #ourpalmerjean #happybirthday #5yearsold #halloweenbaby

E I G H T ✨ I really can’t believe that she made me a mama eight years ago today.

Elliott Grace, you are the light of my life and everything that is good! You are the kindest kid, the best big sister, and the most caring friend. You are beyond smart & you love big. You are a truly wonderful dancer.  I am so very proud of the person you are & I can’t wait to see where life takes you! I am so very lucky to be your mama and that I get a front row seat to the big things you will surely do! Happy 8th birthday my dear! I love you so very much! 🤍

#thisis8 #happybirthday #ourelliottgrace

Hi y’all 👋🏻 I’m Kristyn…

Some words to describe me include:

Mama
Girlfriend
Attorney 
Christian 
Dance mom
Hot mess
Gardener
Cake baker
Taker of photos
Lover of travel
Animal fosterer 

I’m the poster child for having too much on my plate & I’m pretty much a walking contradiction.
I’m trying to slow down but I can’t say no (and don’t want to!)
I vaccinate my kids, feed them happy meals almost weekly but also grow a lot of our own food, can, read labels, and have garlic & honey fermenting in my pantry.
I say I’m going to go to bed early and then stay up scrolling.
I absolutely love my life & am also constantly overstimulated and touched out.
I try to use gentle parenting techniques but also lose my temper daily.
I like it real but also share curated photos.

I don’t fall into any of the “traditional” mom categories and tbh I like it that way. Hopefully I’ve found my way onto the fyp of some other like minded moms (or unlike minded! We need all of us!) so introduce yourself below!
.
.
#fyp #workingmoms #workingmomlife #scrunchy #scrunchymom #sayhi #introduceyourself
